## MAX Width
If screen gets smaller this MQ Rules apply

```css
@media only screen and (max-width: 576px) {
    // do something
}
```
Typically used when you are building from big to small


## MIN Width
If screen gets bigger this MQ Rules apply
```css
@media only screen and (min-width: 576px) {
    // do something
}
```

Typically used when you are building from small to big
